data.description: Welcome to 74 Teaberry Lane, where a serene lifestyle meets convenience. This Elgin, SC home offers a haven on almost an acre of land, complete with a refreshing pool—an outdoor paradise beckoning relaxation.  With a generous $7,000 buyer credit, personalize this charming retreat to your liking. Bask in the tranquility of spacious interiors flooded with natural light, embracing comfort at every turn.  Enjoy the best of suburban living while reveling in the seclusion of lush surroundings. Make 74 Teaberry Lane your retreat and immerse yourself in a life of leisure and endless possibilities.
